Package: cancensus
Type: Package
Title: CensusMapper API Interface to Canada Census
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jens", "von Bergmann", email = "jens@mountainmath.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Dmitry", "Shkolnik", email = "shkolnikd@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Aaron","Jacobs", email = "atheriel@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: The package provides convenient access to StatCan census data via CensusMapper APIs.
    An API key is required to access the data. API keys are available with free registration to CensusMapper at
    https://censusmapper.ca/api
